export const steps = [
  `1. Show a gesture to initiate an answer
   2. Click on the frame to add some examples
   3. Repeat to have a better-trained model
   4. Train the model
   5. Wait some seconds
   5. Click "Next"`,
  `1. After clicking this button you will start a mathematical test
   2. You will have 8 seconds for each question
   3. Show sign that represents an equated answer to answer the question`,
  `1. Enjoy the game :)`,
];
